## � CRITICAL: LIBRARY USAGE POLICY

### STRICT RULE: USE ONLY LEAN IDS COMPONENTS
**NO external UI component libraries allowed in fresh projects.**

Import ONLY from:
- `@lean-ids/components`
- `@lean-ids/tokens`
- `@lean-ids/icons`

### FORBIDDEN IMPORTS:
❌ Material-UI (@mui/material)
❌ Ant Design (antd)
❌ Chakra UI
❌ Bootstrap
❌ Tailwind UI
❌ Shadcn/ui
❌ Radix UI
❌ Mantine
❌ Any other UI library

### EXCEPTION:
✅ If library already exists in package.json, can continue using
✅ If user explicitly says "use only Lean IDS", replace all external components

