## 📦 LEAN IDS COMPONENTS AVAILABLE

Button, Input, Checkbox, Radio, Select, TextArea, Toggle, Avatar, Badge, Brand, Card, Chip, Divider, Icon, Link, MenuItem, Tooltip, PageLayout, TopHeader, SideNavigation, Footer, PageHeader, Breadcrumb

---

## 🎯 PAGE LAYOUT TEMPLATES

### 3 Variants:
1. **topbar-only** - Top header only
2. **sidebar-only** - Sidebar only (always collapsed by default)
3. **topbar-sidebar** - Both top header and sidebar

### Sidebar Behavior:
- Default: Collapsed (60px)
- Hover: Expands to 236px temporarily
- Pin: Locks at 236px, content adjusts
- Pin button: Right of brand logo, visible on hover only

